                           </dimensions>
                        </extent>
                        <collation>
                          <note>Quire descriptions: quires 1–5 balanced; protection quire and quire 7 adjusted balanced; quire 6 unbalanced. Navigation system: black thread sewn into the corner of <locus target="#51" facs="053">fols. 51, </locus> to mark content; yellow thread sewn into the corner of <locus target="#54" facs="056">54</locus> to mark content.</note>
